snippet.title: An Open Letter to Elon Musk Regarding Johnny Depp & Amber Heard (My Quick Take)
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Rant / Elon Musk Rant /Johnny Depp / Amber Heard / Elon Musk / Analysis

In this short video, I share my personal thoughts and feelings on Elon Musk's role in the Depp vs. Heard situation, and I share with Mr. Musk some things that I wish I could say to him in person. 

Just felt like getting a few things off my chest. This is just an informal quick take (or a mini-rant, I'm not sure which), so let me know your thoughts!  I felt inspired to engage in catharsis (with a bit of sarcastic fun thrown in ;). 

I'll have a long video on Depp vs. Heard out this week along with another Marilyn Manson video.
